com.staples.puzzle.bean

Class StaplesReportBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.staples.puzzle.bean.StaplesReportBean

  • public class StaplesReportBean
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to represent the final Analytics Report that includes a) Combined Summary of Staples data for all the Orders b) Combined Summary of Merchant data for all the Orders c) Details of Staples data at the individual Order level d) Details of Merchant data at the individual Order level
    Author:
    KANPR001
